text: Getelo is a community in Bentheim in Lower Saxony. ==Geography== ===Place=== Getelo is west of Nordhorn on the border with the Netherlands. It belongs to the Joint Community (Samtgemeinde) of Uelsen, whose administrative seat is in the like-named community. ===Constituent communities=== The community’s two centres are Getelo and Getelomoor. ==References== ==Other websites== *Joint community’s webpage Category:County of Bentheim (district)
